A basic hellowworld inux device driver.. This will explain major and minor number in the linux device driver.

Please update your Beaglebone board's kernel directory in the Makefile.

Create with linux ubuntuu machine as Host and Target machine as BBB

##for cross compilation 
Build for Beaglebone: sudo make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi-

//Register module
then use insmode and dmesg to insert module and kernel log 

//unregister module
then use rmmode and dmesg to remove module and kernel log
